data.description: Welcome to a little slice of heaven! Extremely cute country home on beautifully landscaped yard with 3 ponds full of fish, gorgeous yard, fenced yard, workshop, RV cover and a single wide mobile home as guest house. Home is located several hundred yards from FM 2610 providing lots of privacy. Home is extremely clean with lots of windows and covered back porch overlooking the ponds. Must really see to appreciate. Great place to retire and/or get away from the city!
